#

Cheesy Potatoes

40 min
$8
350 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Side Dish

Tags:

Comfort FoodSide Dish

Description

Creamy, cheesy potatoes baked to perfection for a comforting side dish.

Ingredients

  • russet potatoes: 4 large
  • cheddar cheese: 2 cups, shredded
  • heavy cream: 1 cup
  • butter: 4 tablespoons
  • salt: 1 teaspoon
  • black pepper: 1/2 teaspoon
  • garlic powder: 1 teaspoon
  • onion powder: 1 teaspoon
